= Front 1929 Movement formed

Baron Rochus von Rheinbaben has reached out to all major liberal organizations in Germany, most importantly the <span style="color: #DCCA4A;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>, left wing of the <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span>, several non-socialist unions and the <span style="color: #D3D3A9;">**JDO**</span> seeking to create a unified republican right. What should our stance on this effort be?

- @support_front_1929: We will support this movement!
- @do_nothing_front_1929: We will do nothing.
- @expel_front_1929: Expel Rheinbaben and his followers!

