With our support, von Rheinbaben has made rapid progress in negotiations for a unified republican right, with official unification expected to come in coming months.

@do_nothing_front_1929

With our lukewarm support to Rheinbaben's initiative, attempts to form a unified republican right party have faltered. However our discussion with the <span style="color: #DCCA4A;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> over the cource of the movement has strengthened our ties, bringing the creation of a unifed liberal party closer then ever.

