With our rejection of Von Rheinbaben's initiative the effort for republican unity quickly collapsed. Our rejection of the Front has enraged our liberal and labor wings, and torched our relations with the <span style="color: #DCCA4A;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>.

However our rejection has strengthened our ties with the national opposition and greatly enhanced our nationalist credentials.
